类 DocTreePath

  • java.lang.Object
    • source.util.DocTreePath
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Iterable<DocTree>

    @Exported
public class DocTreePath
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<DocTree>
    A path of tree nodes, typically used to represent the sequence of ancestor nodes of a tree node up to the top level DocCommentTree node.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.8
